===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-stumble.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌmbəl|-ʌmbəl]]

===Noun===
'''stumble'''
#a [[fall]] or [[trip]]
#an [[error]] or [[blunder]]

===Intransitive verb===
'''to stumble''' ([[stumbles]], [[stumbled]], [[stumbling]])

#to [[trip]] or [[fall]]
#:''He '''stumbled''' over a rock.''
#to make a [[mistake]] or have [[trouble]]
#:''I always '''stumble''' over verbs in Spanish.''
#to [[find]] by [[accident]]; to [[happen]] upon (especially with '''across''' or '''upon''')
#:''I went to the store and '''stumbled''' across an old friend.''

